i.client_search_query_parse_no_encipher"}, {"applicable_scenario": "attr", "description": "API endpoint: POST /api/v1/fields/retrieve (retrieve_fields) — RAG 字段检索接口\n\n根据自然语言查询，从知识库中召回最相关的字段意图，\n返回字段定义及可直接注入 LLM Prompt 的文本段落。\n\nArgs:\n    request: 包含 query（查询文本）和 top_k（返回数量）\n\nReturns:\n    匹配的字段意图列表及格式化的 prompt 片段", "has_execute_fn": true, "parameters": {"properties": {"body": {"description": "请求体 JSON", "type": "object"}, "request": {"description": "参数 request", "type": "string"}}, "required": ["request"], "type": "object"}, "tool_id": "client_search.api.retrieve_fields"}]}}, "project_info": {"description": "将客户搜索项目作为通用评估系统的第一个项目适配实现。", "name": "客户搜索评估示例", "project_id": "client_search"}, "reference_panel": {"actual": {"conditions": [{"field": "pCategorys", "operator": "MATCH", "value": "年金保险"}], "query_logic": "AND"}, "reference": {"empty_result_reason": "", "external_boundary_sources": {"config_paths": {"source_enhanced_rules": "/Users/xiaozijian/WorkSpace/projects/claude_code/llm_client_search_0513/llm_client_search/src/main/python/config/enhanced_rules_args.yaml", "source_field_definitions": "/Users/xiaozijian/WorkSpace/projects/claude_code/llm_client_search_0513/llm_client_search/src/main/python/config/field_definitions_args.yaml", "source_field_enums": "/Users/xiaozijian/WorkSpace/projects/claude_code/llm_client_search_0513/llm_client_search/src/main/python/config/field_enums_args.yaml", "source_value_mappings": "/Users/xiaozijian/WorkSpace/projects/claude_code/llm_client_search_0513/llm_client_search/src/main/python/config/value_mappings_args.yaml"}}, "is_empty_result": false, "logic": "AND", "matched_level": 4, "matched_patterns": "### 当前时间\n2026-07-03 11:51:46 (Asia/Shanghai)\n### 今天星期\n周五\n\n### 相关字段参考（根据查询内容动态召回）\n\n\n- **isBuyInsurance** | 操作符: CONTAINS | 值类型: enum | 枚举: ['\''客户'\'', '\''准客'\'', '\''用户'\''] | 定义: 客户类型；客户/准客=买过保险，用户=没有买过保险 | 说明: 客户=已签约，准客=潜在客户已接触，用户=未购买；买过保险→客户或准客，没有买过保险→用户\n\n  示例: \"有保险的客户\" → {\"field\": \"isBuyInsurance\", \"operat